<p>Welcome to AB LEGO, your premier destination for LEGO sets. We are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring that your personal information is handled in a safe and responsible manner. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, process, and protect your information, in compliance with the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR).</p>
