<p>Personal Identification Information: Name, email address, phone number, shipping address, birthdate, gender, age.</p>
<p>Payment Information: Credit card details, billing address. Note: Payment information is processed by our secure payment processors and is not stored on our servers.</p>
<p>Web Usage Information: IP address, web browser type, pages visited, and cookies, to enhance your experience and improve our services.</p>
<br />

<p>2. How We Use Your Information</p>
<br />
<p>Your information is used for the following purposes:</p>


<p>To process and fulfill your orders.</p>

